    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. Looking at the environmental side specifically, some experts are saying it's pretty much a non-negotiable tool if we're going to meet climate goals. Do you see any actual viable alternatives to congestion pricing for hitting those emission targets in a city that big?",
